snippet.title: Real Story of Dunki | How Indians Cross US Mexico Border? | Donkey Process | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
🤖 Join the Master ChatGPT - Full Course : https://academy.dhruvrathee.com/chatgpt
Learn to harness the power of ChatGPT to transform your life! 
Use coupon code: DUN40 for 40% discount! Offer only valid for the first 400 people. 

In this video by Dhruv Rathee, the focus is on the heart-wrenching story of illegal immigration from India, specifically the tragic journey of a family from the small village of Dingucha, Gujarat. The video delves into the realities of "donkey flights," a term for illegal immigration routes, and the dangerous journeys families undertake for a better life in countries like the USA ,UK and Canada. It also explores the broader context of why people risk everything, including political and economic factors, and the role of misleading agents in this perilous process. Donkey Process of illegal immigration has also inspired the story of the movie "Dunki" starring Shah Rukh Khan. Watch as Dhruv Rathee sheds light on this critical issue, blending personal stories with broader social and political insights.

Link to the mentioned video - 
Dark Reality of Jawan Film | Shah Rukh Khan | Dhruv Rathee - https://youtu.be/HodJLhRV7gY?si=DTUduLxyP6KfnWv3

snippet.title: Khumar Episode 10 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - 23rd December 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 10 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 23rd December 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz
Neelam Muneer as Hareem
Hina Bayat as Kehkasha Begum
Asma Abbas as Durdana
Behroz Sabzwari as Sheikh Furqan
Zainab Qayoom as Dil Araa
Shehryar Zaidi as Taufeeq
Adnan Samad as Nasir
Sheherzade Peerzada as Hamna  
Minsa Malik as Laiba 
Kinza Malik as Atiya
Mehmood Akhtar as Zaawar  
Agha Mustafa as Rayyan  
Hamzah Tariq as Rufi
Ayesha Rajpoot as Shagufta
Mizna Waqas as Husna
Sohail Masood as Mirza Sahab
Birjees Farooqui as Salma

snippet.description:

snippet.title: Khumar Episode 09 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - 22nd December 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 09 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 22nd December 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz
Neelam Muneer as Hareem
Hina Bayat as Kehkasha Begum
Asma Abbas as Durdana

Hamzah Tariq as Rufi

snippet.title: Popatlal है Taarak का 'Favorite Uncle' |Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah |Giggles At Gada Electronics
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Jetha comes to the soda shop and asks Abdul to serve double soda to everyone. Taarak asks him if there is any special occasion but he says that Tapu has been studying the whole day. Bhide and Sodhi join him too as they share that their kids are doing the same too. Later, Tapu Sena feels guilty of hiding their suspension from their parents.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1077
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2023 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.description:

Crafted against the evocative backdrop of a sampled melody from the legendary Punjabi singer Laal Chand Yamla Jatt, this musical masterpiece vividly depicts DIVINE's innermost thoughts and emotions. Produced by the duo Zzorawar and Arsh Heer, the beats resonate with the hauntingly beautiful verses of Yamla Jatt's classic, 'Tere Ni Karara Mainu Puteya,Das Main Ki Pyar Wichon Kuhteya' which translates to 'Your promises cost me dearly, tell me what did I gain from love.' This sample threads through the rhythm, infusing the track with an emotional depth that perfectly aligns with DIVINE's lyrical narrative.

snippet.title: Main ATAL Hoon - Trailer | Pankaj Tripathi | Ravi Jadhav | Vinod Bhanushali | 19 Jan 2024
snippet.description:
More than a poet. More than a statesman. More than a Prime Minister. Presenting the trailer of #MainATALHoon. 

Vinod Bhanushali presents, Main ATAL Hoon, a film on the extraordinary life of the leader you knew but the man you didn't, starring National Award winner Pankaj Tripathi. 

Directed by National Awardee Ravi Jadhav, and written by Rishi Virmani and Ravi Jadhav, "Main ATAL Hoon" presented by Bhanushali Studios Limited and Legend Studios, is produced by Vinod Bhanushali, Sandeep Singh, and Kamlesh Bhanushali.
The film releases on 19th January 2024 in cinemas near you. 


CREDITS:

Starring : Pankaj Tripathi
Director : Ravi Jadhav
Producers : Vinod Bhanushali, Sandeep Singh and Kamlesh Bhanushali
Co Producer - Bhavesh Bhanushali, Sam Khan
Cinematographer : Lawrence DCunha
Story, Screenplay and Dialogues - Rishi Virmani & Ravi Jadhav 
BGM : Monty Sharma 
Editor : Bunty Nagi 
Music : Salim - Sulaiman, Payal Dev, Kailash Kher, Amitraj
Production Designer : Sandeep Ravade

snippet.title: Jethalal का नही रहा अपने गुस्से पर काबू | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 19 Dec 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Tapu Sena decides to go on a hunger strike if they do not get the season cricket kit from their parents. This causes Jetha and others to get worried. What will they do?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 616
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: MEENAKSHI Full Movie | 2023 New Released Hindi Dubbed Movie | Regina Cassandra, Vennela Kishore
snippet.description:
Here's presenting "MEENAKSHI" the Hindi Dubbed Version of the Telugu action thriller mystery Film "NENE NAA", starring Regina Cassandra, Vennela Kishore, and Akshara Gowda in lead roles 

#meenakshi #nenenaa #reginacassandra 

Movie: Meenakshi  
Original Movie:- Nene Naa
Director:- Caarthick Raju 
StarCast:- Regina Cassandra, Vennela Kishore, Akshara Gowda
Presented By: RKD Studios 
Music:- Sam C.S

The film is set in two periods, the present and the 1920s. In modern times an archaeologist, as part of her job, unearths something antique which leads to mysterious events.

A foreigner is attacked and sucked into quicksand by an ethereal force. Archaeologist heroine Divya explores the situation and discovers a 120-year-old woman's skeleton. Shortly after that, the forensic reports say that the skull's facial features resemble those of Divya. Shortly after the local DSP was brutally murdered with a spear perched into him.

The forensic report identifies fingerprints on the spear that are consistent with those of a young woman. Heroine Divya tells her brother, who is assaulted by a lady who resembles her sister, about the bizarre occurrences.

snippet.description:

Episode 3961: Sodhi Aur Roshan Ki Sulha
--------------------------------------------------------
Sodhi apologizes to his wife, but Roshan appears displeased and refuses to accept his apologies. Sodhi is ultimately persuaded when he talks about his heartbroken state following Roshan's departure. Bhide was chastised by all the Gokuldham men for revealing the truth. Bhide explains his actions by claiming that he was almost caught by Sodhi's wife and thus had no choice but to tell the truth.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3961, 22 Dec 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Episode No - 365
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

About MaaTri Media 

MaaTri, represents the most beautiful relationship between a mother and a daughter - Nisha Topwal & Anantya Anand aka. MyMissAnand. MaaTri is formed through a combination of two Hindi words - Maa (Mother) and PuTri (daughter) that brings forth energy, enthusiasm and determination to spread positive vibes through their outstanding content. Their content revolves around fashion, food, comedy, parenting, travel, glimpse of their family and simple day-to-day activities that both enjoy doing together. 
The duo captures a contemporary lifestyle of entrepreneur and food blogger mom and a teenage daughter and a social media influencer and shows how they both manage their work, school and personal life - simple pleasure of growing together, through engaging videos and fun visuals. Every post is curated and designed to make the audience laugh, learn, smile and entertain. 

#MyMissAnand #WinterSpecial #typesofkids  #Winter #ChotivsbadiBehen #Behen #TeenagervsKids #FamilyDrama #winterspecial #FamilyVideo #Family #mymissanand #cookwithnisha #christmas #santaclaus

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2 | Flowers | EP# 415
snippet.description:
സിദ്ധാര്‍ഥിന്റെ കുടുംബത്തില്‍ നടക്കുന്ന കല്യാണത്തിന് പോകാന്‍ തയ്യാറെടുക്കുകയാണ് പാറമട വീട്ടുകാര്‍. കല്യാണത്തിന് പോകുന്നതിനായി ബാലുവിനെ കാത്തിരിക്കുകയാണ്. എല്ലാവരെയും ഞെട്ടിച്ചുകൊണ്ട് ബാലു വീണ്ടും ഗുണ്ട ലുക്കില്‍ എത്തുകയാണ്.


Paramada family is getting ready to attend the wedding at Siddharthan's house. Everyone is waiting for Balu. Surprisingly, Balu appears at Rowdy attire again.

snippet.title: Malya ने Tapu Sena से किया छोटे Bat की माँग | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Endless Jetha
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to the Sony LIV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv


Tapu Sena invites a poor boy called Malaya to Gokuldham society. Took him to Goli's house where Komal offered him and the Tapu Sena hot samosas. They played cricket with Malaya and later met his parents. Stay tuned in to learn more about this episode.



Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Mandar Chandwadkar, Munmun Dutta, Bhavya Gandhi, Amit Bhatt, Sonalika Joshi, Tanuj Mahashabde, Shyam Pathak, Sailesh Lodha, Neha Mehta, Gurcharan Singh, Mayur Vakani, Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonyliv #comedy #comedy2023 #jethalal #jethalalcomedy 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

#tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3960 | 21 Dec 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3960: Roshan Ghar Chor Kar Mat Jao
--------------------------------------------------------
Champaklal tries to seize Jethalal the instant he follows in the footsteps of Gokuldham society. Jethalal feels intimidated and runs from his father. Champaklal chastises Jethalal for assisting Sodhi in hiding from his wife. Champaklal is informed by Jethalal that he was never connected with Sodhi and instead went out to meet Nattu Kaka. Later, Sodhi's wife decides to return to her parents' home permanently.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3960, 21 Dec 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

Episode 120: Aradhna's Trust
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Jai and his family members arrive to live at Aradhna's house when they lose everything. Later, Aradhna confronts Reyansh and asks him to leave her and her family alone. Now, stay tuned to know how Aradhana will return to her normal state and what steps Reyansh will take to get her back to his life.

Show Name: Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka
Cast: Shivangi Joshi, Kushal Tandon, Nausheen Ali Sardar, Simba Nagpal
Episode: 120
Director: Atif Khan
Producer: Ekta Kapoor

About Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Kaa:
------------------------------------------------------------
A sensible and ambitious journalist joins a media company run by a suave maverick man. While united in their passion for honest and ground-breaking journalism, their contrasting characters immediately put them at loggerheads. What will happen when she starts falling in love with him despite the red flags? 'Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka' stars Shivangi Joshi and Kushal Tandon in lead roles.

Now, stay tuned to know how Aradhana will return to her normal state and what steps Reyansh will take to get her back to his life.
